p.span:
1. Define Target & Objective
- What do you need to know?
- Define output:
map, timeline & network

div.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
3.
Lay Psychological Foundation
- Analyze tone
&
sentiment NLP
- Track behavioral cues
&
timing

div.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
2.
Collect OSINT
&
SOCMINT
- Gather public data:
news, filings, govt
- Scrape social media SOCMINT

div.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
3c.
Digital Biography
Gather IDs, emails,
social profiles & posts

div.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
3d.
Analyze Behavioral Patterns
Find patterns in time, topics & networks

div.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
3e.
Assess Competencies
&
Affinities
Technical skill
&
privacy awareness

div.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
4.
Acquire IMINT
- Satellite:
Google Earth, Bing
- Drone:
Legal flights only
- On-foot:
Public photography

div.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
5.
Reverse Image & Metadata
- Run image(s)
through search engines
- Inspect EXIF data
- Check historical archives

div.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
6.
Cross-Reference with Maps
- Pin images to
geospatial tools
- Match with Street View
- Detect changes over time

div.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
7.
Verification & Triangulation
- Correlate:
OSINT, SOCMINT, IMINT
- Flag contradictions for review
- Never trust a single source

div.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
8.
Compile & Report Findings
- Synthesize into
timeline & map
- List key findings & risks

div.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
9.
Counter-OSINT Audit
- Strip metadata from your files
- Audit your own digital footprint
- Monitor for self-leaks

div.style: color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
10.
Counter-Intelligence
Privacy Hardening,
Disinformation
&
SOCMINT Monitoring

span.p:
12.
Finalize & Secure Report
- Encrypt & secure report
